OpenWrt-libtool: compile:  ccache_cc -DHAVE_CONFIG_H -I. -I ./include -I ./include -I ./lib -I ./lib -I/openwrt/staging_dir/target-x86_64_musl/usr/include -DNDEBUG -I/openwrt/staging_dir/toolchain-x86_64_gcc-8.4.0_musl/usr/include -I/openwrt/staging_dir/toolchain-x86_64_gcc-8.4.0_musl/include/fortify -I/openwrt/staging_dir/toolchain-x86_64_gcc-8.4.0_musl/include -Wstrict-prototypes -Wall -Wextra -Wno-sign-compare -Wpointer-arith -Wformat -Wformat-security -Wswitch-enum -Wunused-parameter -Wbad-function-cast -Wcast-align -Wstrict-prototypes -Wold-style-definition -Wmissing-prototypes -Wmissing-field-initializers -fno-strict-aliasing -Wswitch-bool -Wlogical-not-parentheses -Wsizeof-array-argument -Wbool-compare -Wshift-negative-value -Wduplicated-cond -Wshadow -Wmultistatement-macros -Wcast-align=strict -fomit-frame-pointer -Os -pipe -fno-caller-saves -fno-plt -fhonour-copts -Wno-error=unused-but-set-variable -Wno-error=unused-result -fmacro-prefix-map=/openwrt/build_dir/target-x86_64_musl/linux-x86_64/openvswitch-2.15.0=openvswitch-2.15.0 -Wformat -Werror=format-security -fstack-protector -D_FORTIFY_SOURCE=1 -Wl,-z,now -Wl,-z,relro -flto -std=gnu99 -DHAVE_AVX512F -DHAVE_LD_AVX512_GOOD -MT lib/sha1.lo -MD -MP -MF lib/.deps/sha1.Tpo -c lib/sha1.c  -fPIC -DPIC -o lib/.libs/sha1.o
